                    Specifies the value whose bits to scan.
                </p></dd></dl></div></div><div class="refsect1"><a id="description"></a><h2>Description</h2><p>
            <code class="function">findLSB</code> returns the bit number of the least significant bit that is set to 1 in the binary
            representation of <em class="parameter"><code>value</code></em>. If <em class="parameter"><code>value</code></em> is zero, -1 will be returned.
